        "content": "<p>As in the title, I'd like to iterate through all possible functions <code>f : α → β</code> where <code>Fintype α</code> and <code>Fintype β</code>.<br>\nThe goal is to return <code>true</code> if there is no <code>f</code> which <code>g : (α → β) → Bool</code> returns <code>false</code>, or <code>false</code> otherwise.<br>\nHow should I achieve this?</p>",
